userdoc.notice: A hook for a pool that allows a Uniswap pool to act as an oracle. Pools that use this hook must have full range     tick spacing and liquidity is always permanently locked in these pools. This is the suggested configuration     for protocols that wish to use a V3 style geomean oracle.
